data.title: england.world – British, Subculture inspired since 1981
data.text:
Authentic. British. Sub-Culture Inspired. Since 1981

We are an independent British owned company.

A subculture champion, that was born out of a love of renegade style

A touchstone for those for whom style is synonymous with intelligence, independence and rebellious spirit.

Always Forward, Never Back…..

The Original Creeper has been ever present in our collection since the 1980s. As well as the classic Wulfrun Creepers in Leather and Suede, we produce limited batches of material and colour combinations. We have released some for the site launch and these are available directly from stock for immediate shipping.

Available from stock and ready to ship

Winklepickers, were originally known as “poulaines” when these shoes were worn as a fashion and social statement. The longer the point of your shoe – then the higher your social status. The term Winklepicker was derived from using a sharp, pointed object to prise the sea-winkle from its shell.

The Underground Winklepicker Shoe and Boots styles uses an original 1950’s last shape on these classic Allgender styles.

We now offers all of the Classic Winklepickers directly from stock and ready to ship
